# Multi-Model Selection Implementation Plan

The goal is to allow users to select different Gemini models in the chat interface. This provides a workaround when a specific model reaches its quota (429 Too Many Requests error).

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> I will be adding a list of available Gemini models. Please confirm if you would like specific models included or excluded. I am starting with:
> - `gemini-2.0-flash`
> - `gemini-1.5-flash`
> - `gemini-1.5-flash-8b`
> - `gemini-1.5-pro`

